OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774717866
OL,3,COwner of XL bully dog which killed
OL,4,Cpensioner 'devastated' by incident
OL,6,FThe owner of an XL bully which savaged
OL,7,Fa pensioner has told a court he would
OL,8,Fnot wish the attack on his "worst
OL,9,Fenemy".
OL,11,FJohn McColl, 84, died from his
OL,12,Finjuries a month after the attack by
OL,13,Fthe dog, called Toretto, which had to
OL,14,Fbe shot 10 times by armed police
OL,15,Fofficers who were called to the scene
OL,16,Fin Warrington, Cheshire, in February
OL,17,F2025.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
