OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774717866
OL,3,COwner of XL bully dog which killed
OL,4,Cpensioner 'devastated' by incident
OL,6,FGiving evidence at Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Friday, owner Sean Garner
OL,8,Fsaid he took every step he possibly
OL,9,Fcould to make sure the dog was safe.
OL,11,FHe claimed the dog was locked inside a
OL,12,Fshed on the patio outside his home on
OL,13,FBardsley Avenue, which had a gate he
OL,14,Fsaid was secured by a latch and a
OL,15,Fchain, when Mr McColl wandered up the
OL,16,Fdriveway at about 6pm on 24 February
OL,17,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774717866
OL,3,COwner of XL bully dog which killed
OL,4,Cpensioner 'devastated' by incident
OL,6,FGarner said: "I could never imagine
OL,7,Fthat a man who has been the pub could
OL,8,Fgo up my path on his way home and do
OL,9,Fwhat he has obviously done to let my
OL,10,Fdog out."
OL,12,FHe said he was "devastated" by the
OL,13,Fincident.
OL,15,FGarner added: "It's horrible what's
OL,16,Fhappened to him.
OL,18,F"I've got no words to describe what
OL,19,Fhappened to him. I wouldn't wish it on
OL,20,Fmy worst enemy."
OL,26,@nD@NOUrD@IO]tD@POUtD@[O]wD@OOUzD@AOU|D@
OL,26,APO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774717866
OL,3,COwner of XL bully dog which killed
OL,4,Cpensioner 'devastated' by incident
OL,6,FGarner disagreed that the dog was
OL,7,Fhungry, despite an examination finding
OL,8,Fthere was no dog food in its stomach.
OL,10,FHe said: "Someone's come into his
OL,11,Fproperty who he doesn't know. It's
OL,12,Fnatural behaviour of a dog."
OL,14,FDavid Birrell, prosecuting, said:
OL,15,F"Your dog wasn't guarding the
OL,16,Fpremises, it was eating Mr McColl."
OL,18,FGarner replied: "He was locked in the
OL,19,Fshed when I went out."
OL,26,@rD@JOUtD@\O]wD@AOUxD@cO]zD@QOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774717866
OL,3,COwner of XL bully dog which killed
OL,4,Cpensioner 'devastated' by incident
OL,6,FThe 31-year-old, who the court heard
OL,7,Fran a recovery business transporting
OL,8,Fcars, said he did not return to his
OL,9,Fhome when police rang him about the
OL,10,Fincident because he was disqualified
OL,11,Ffrom driving and did not want officers
OL,12,Fto see him in a vehicle.
OL,14,FHe agreed he was a "coward" to instead
OL,15,Fallow his pregnant partner to return
OL,16,Fto the house with their two children,
OL,17,Fwhich led to police arresting her.
OL,19,FGarner said: "I was waiting to find
OL,20,Fout what had happened."
OL,26,@vD@TOUvD@[O]{D@NOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774717866
OL,3,COwner of XL bully dog which killed
OL,4,Cpensioner 'devastated' by incident
OL,6,FThe prosecution allege the dog was not
OL,7,Flocked inside the shed but was on the
OL,8,Fpatio of the home, with only a latch
OL,9,Fon the gate preventing it from getting
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,FGarner, of Belle Vale, Liverpool,
OL,13,Fdenies being the owner of a dog which
OL,14,Fcaused injury while dangerously out of
OL,15,Fcontrol.
OL,17,FHe has previously admitted two counts
OL,18,Fof possessing an XL bully without an
OL,19,Fexemption certificate relating to
OL,20,FToretto and a female dog, called
OL,21,FMalibu, found inside the house.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
